    }\n    code {\n      background: var(--code);\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      padding: 1px 5px;\n      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace;\n      font-size: 0.94em;\n    }\n    ul, ol {\n      margin: 8px 0;\n      padding-left: 22px;\n    }\n    li { margin: 5px 0; }\n    .meta {\n      color: var(--muted);\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n    .cards {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));\n      gap: 12px;\n      margin-top: 16px;\n    }\n    .card {\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 14px;\n      background: #fbfcfe;\n    }\n    .card strong {\n      display: block;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      margin-bottom: 6px;\n    }\n    .card span {\n      display: block;\n      font-size: 20px;\n      font-weight: 760;\n    }\n    .bad { color: var(--red); }\n    .warn { color: var(--amber); }\n    .ok { color: var(--green); }\n    .note {\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);\n      padding: 10px 12px;\n      background: #eef5ff;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      margin-top: 12px;\n    }\n    .note.warn {\n      border-left-color: var(--amber);\n      background: #fff5db;\n    }\n    .note.bad {\n      border-left-color: var(--red);\n      background: #fdeeee;\n    }\n    .tag {\n      display: inline-block;\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      padding: 2px 8px;\n      font-size: 12px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      background: #eef2f7;\n      color: #39445a;\n      white-space: nowrap;\n    }\n    .tag.bad { background: #fdeeee; color: var(--red); }\n    .tag.warn { background: #fff5db; color: var(--amber); }\n    .tag.ok { background: #e9f7ef; color: var(--green); }\n    .tag.info { background: #e7f0ff; color: var(--blue); }\n    .small { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }\n    a { color: var(--blue); }\n    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n    .child-link {\n      font-weight: 650;\n      text-decoration: none;\n      border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--blue);\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 900px) {\n      main { padding: 24px 14px 42px; }\n      .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n      table { font-size: 13px; }\n      th, td { padding: 8px; }\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 560px) {\n      .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<main>\n  <header>\n    <h1>Body-Tell 与 VoxTell 论文不一致项总控计划</h1>\n    <p class=\"meta\">日期：2026-05-24。范围：<code>VoxTell/VoxTell.pdf</code>、<code>VoxTell/</code> 官方实现/权重计划、当前 <code>Body-Tell/</code> 训练相关代码与配置。根目录 <code>train.py</code> 未纳入。</p>\n    <div class=\"cards\">\n      <div class=\"card\"><strong>明确不一致</strong><span class=\"bad\">13 项</span></div>\n      <div class=\"card\"><strong>已分发到子计划</strong><span class=\"ok\">13 项</span></div>\n      <div class=\"card\"><strong>已起草子计划</strong><span class=\"ok\">3 个</span></div>\n      <div class=\"card\"><strong>总体判断</strong><span class=\"warn\">可执行，待实施（2026-05-24 修订）</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"note warn\">2026-05-24 修订：原 11 项基础上新增 #12 BCE+Dice loss 等价性、#13 <code>num_heads</code> mismatch（Body-Tell=32 vs VoxTell=1）。其中 #13 同时修正了原 SP-A 中\"VoxTell projection 输出 <code>[32,2048,4096,8192,10240]</code>\"的错误表述（实际为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320]</code> 量级，<code>num_heads</code> 才是根因）。</p>\n    <div class=\"note warn\"><strong>域差异豁免（2026-05-24 重要约束）</strong>：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid，VoxTell 处理医学影像（CT/MRI/PET）。任务输入模态、特征统计、噪声特性都不同。<strong>本计划中\"对齐\"是手段不是目的，目的是支持 VoxTell 权重复用与实现一致性。任何一项不一致，若实现阶段 audit 后发现对齐会损害性能、或对当前任务没有可观察收益、或与权重复用无关，允许显式跳过并在子计划中记录原因。</strong> #12（loss 公式）与 #13（<code>num_heads</code>）尤其适用此豁免。</div>\n  </header>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>使用方式</h2>\n    <p>本文件是父级执行总控，只回答三件事：先做什么、每个差异由哪个子计划负责、什么时候可以进入下一阶段。代码级方案、测试命令和参数细节以三个子计划为准。</p>\n    <p class=\"note\">域适配差异（输入模态、patch size、augmentation、global batch、数据/词表规模等）视为 Body-Tell 前提，不作为本轮整改目标。本轮只处理可在 Body-Tell 域内对齐的模型结构、数据构造和训练机制。</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>子计划索引</h2>\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>编号</th>\n          <th>子计划</th>\n          <th>关注范围</th>\n          <th>状态</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>SP-A</td>\n          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</a></td>\n          <td>模型结构对齐：transformer decoder 语义、ResidualEncoder、VoxTellDecoder、5-scale projection、位置编码策略、VoxTell 权重加载入口、训练实验矩阵。</td>\n          <td><span class=\"tag ok\">已起草</span></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>SP-B</td>\n          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_sampling_vocabulary_optimization_report.html\">Body-Tell Sampling 与 Vocabulary 优化思路</a></td>\n          <td>数据构造对齐：动态采样基础设施、85% foreground patch oversampling、patch 内 2+1 prompt、25/75 canonical/variant、aggregate sampler、vocabulary expansion、text embedding 重建。</td>\n          <td><span class=\"tag ok\">已起草</span></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>SP-C</td>\n          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_training_loop_eval_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">Body-Tell 训练机制与评估协议对齐计划</a></td>\n          <td>训练循环对齐：fixed-update epoch/iteration 节奏、SGD + polynomial decay、deep supervision 5-scale loss 权重、checkpoint/scheduler resume、prompt robustness / negative / held-out 评估协议、paper-aligned 测试矩阵。</td>\n          <td><span class=\"tag ok\">已起草</span></td>\n        </tr>\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_3","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,260p' Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P5-P6-lite/REVIEW.html\"","aggregated_output":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <title>SP-A.P5-P6-lite Review</title>\n  <style>\n    body { margin: 0; background: #f6f8fa; color: #17202a; font: 15px/1.55 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif; }\n    main { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px 56px; }\n    section { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #d8e0e7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px 20px; margin: 16px 0; }\n    h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 28px; }\n    h2 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 20px; }\n    table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 14px; }\n    th, td { border: 1px solid #d8e0e7; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }\n    th { background: #eef3f7; }\n    code, pre { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace; }\n    code { background: #edf3f7; border-radius: 4px; padding: 1px 4px; }\n    pre { overflow-x: auto; background: #111827; color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px; }\n    .meta { color: #5d6875; }\n    .ok { color: #276749; font-weight: 700; }\n    .fail { color: #b42318; font-weight: 700; }\n    .warn { color: #9a4a17; font-weight: 700; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<main>\n  <header>\n    <h1>SP-A.P5-P6-lite Review</h1>\n    <p class=\"meta\">Reviewed source plan: <code>Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html</code>. Worker result: <code>Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P5-P6-lite/RESULT.html</code>.</p>\n    <p><strong>Verdict:</strong> <span class=\"fail\">needs_fix</span></p>\n  </header>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>Summary</h2>\n    <p>The prefix-only VoxTell transformer decoder loader and non-cubic HWD flatten coverage are implemented and verified by local tests/audit. However, the required phase1 Slurm gate failed, so this task cannot be accepted. I also reproduced a runtime dtype contract failure under CUDA bfloat16 autocast: <code>memory</code> becomes <code>bfloat16</code> while the generated <code>pos</code> tensor is <code>float32</code>.</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>Acceptance Evidence</h2>\n    <table>\n      <thead><tr><th>Status</th><th>Criterion</th><th>Evidence</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>P5 is not an independent <code>pos_embed</code> implementation stage.</td><td>The source plan says P5 is folded into P6-lite. The diff updates runtime position generation in <code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py</code> and does not add a separate P5/fixed position stage.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>Do not implement <code>fixed_voxtell_192</code> and do not add a <code>pos_embed</code> state-dict loading path.</td><td>No <code>fixed_voxtell_192</code> implementation was found in the diff. The loader filters only keys beginning with <code>transformer_decoder.</code>; <code>pos_embed</code> is listed only in excluded metadata.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"fail\">Fail</td><td>Runtime position encoding is generated from the selected feature's actual H,W,D and matches memory token count, batch, dtype, device, and channel dimension.</td><td>The full-precision/unit-test path passes shape/device checks, but a CUDA AMP smoke failed the dtype part of this contract: <code>memory dtype=torch.bfloat16</code>, <code>pos dtype=torch.float32</code>. See command output below.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>Non-cubic input coverage verifies <code>b c d h w -&gt; b h w d c -&gt; (h w d) b c</code>.</td><td><code>test_runtime_memory_and_pos_use_voxtell_hwd_flatten_contract</code> captures projected bottleneck and transformer memory using a non-cubic input. The local pytest run passed.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>Loader reads <code>fold_0/checkpoint_final.pth</code> <code>network_weights</code> and filters only <code>transformer_decoder.*</code> keys.</td><td><code>load_voxtell_transformer_decoder_prefix()</code> resolves directories to <code>fold_0/checkpoint_final.pth</code>, requires <code>network_weights</code>, and builds <code>source_state</code> only from <code>transformer_decoder.</code> keys.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>Filtered keys map exactly to <code>model.transformer_decoder.state_dict()</code> with no missing, unexpected, or shape mismatch entries.</td><td>The CPU audit reported 110 tensors, 251,858,944 loaded params, 0 missing, 0 unexpected, and 0 shape mismatches.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>Loading uses <code>model.transformer_decoder.load_state_dict(..., strict=True)</code>.</td><td>The implementation calls <code>model.transformer_decoder.load_state_dict(source_state, strict=True)</code> after exact key and shape validation.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>Loader explicitly does not load <code>encoder.*</code>, <code>decoder.*</code>, projectors, or <code>pos_embed</code>; no full-model whitelist is used.</td><td>The loader has a hard <code>transformer_decoder.</code> prefix check and no full-model whitelist path. The unit test includes non-prefix encoder/decoder/projector/<code>pos_embed</code> keys and verifies projector weights remain unchanged.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>Logs and saved checkpoint config record <code>init_transformer_from_voxtell</code> metadata: checkpoint path, prefix, loaded tensor count, and loaded parameter count.</td><td><code>Body-Tell/train.py</code> writes the loader metadata into <code>cfg[\"init_transformer_from_voxtell\"]</code>, logs checkpoint/prefix/tensor/parameter counts, and saves <code>cfg</code> in <code>best.pt</code>, smoke checkpoints, and <code>last.pt</code>.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"ok\">Pass</td><td>CPU prefix audit passes.</td><td>Reviewer run of <code>Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code> passed with the expected transformer decoder prefix counts.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"fail\">Fail</td><td>At least one forward/loss/backward smoke passes if GPU is available.</td><td>CUDA is available on <code>NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4090</code>. The reviewer AMP smoke failed before backward due the position dtype mismatch. The worker result records a non-AMP smoke pass, but the required phase1 gate is AMP-enabled and cannot currently pass.</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>Commands Run</h2>\n    <pre>conda run -n voxtell python -m pytest Body-Tell/tests/test_model_shapes.py\n\ncollected 10 items\nBody-Tell/tests/test_model_shapes.py .......... [100%]\n10 passed in 16.36s</pre>\n\n    <pre>conda run -n voxtell python Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py --config Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_aligned.yaml\n\nTransformer decoder prefix audit\n  status: PASS\n  prefix: transformer_decoder.\n  loaded tensors: 110\n  loaded params: 251,858,944\n  missing: 0\n  unexpected: 0\n  shape mismatches: 0</pre>\n\n    <pre>conda run -n voxtell python -c \"import torch; print(torch.cuda.is_available()); print(torch.cuda.get_device_name(0) if torch.cuda.is_available() else 'no cuda')\"\n\nTrue\nNVIDIA GeForce RTX 4090</pre>\n\n    <pre>conda run -n voxtell python -c \"[build aligned model, load VoxTell prefix, CUDA bfloat16 autocast forward/loss/backward smoke]\"\n\nRuntimeError: runtime position encoding contract violated:\nmemory shape=(64, 1, 2048) dtype=torch.bfloat16 device=cuda:0;\npos shape=(64, 1, 2048) dtype=torch.float32 device=cuda:0</pre>\n\n    <pre>git diff --check -- Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py Body-Tell/train.py Body-Tell/tests/test_model_shapes.py Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py\n\npassed with no output</pre>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>Phase1 Slurm Gate</h2>\n    <pre>Phase1 Slurm gate: failed\nSlurm command: sbatch slurm/body-tell-phase1.sh\nSlurm job id: 37775\nsacct final state: FAILED\nsacct exit code: 1:0</pre>\n    <p><strong>Phase1 Slurm gate:</strong> <span class=\"fail\">failed</span></p>\n    <p><strong>Slurm command:</strong> <code>sbatch slurm/body-tell-phase1.sh</code></p>\n    <p><strong>Slurm job id:</strong> <code>37775</code></p>\n    <p><strong>sacct final state:</strong> <code>FAILED</code></p>\n    <p><strong>sacct exit code:</strong> <code>1:0</code></p>\n    <pre>sacct -j 37775 --format=JobID,State,ExitCode,Elapsed -n\n\n37775            FAILED      1:0   00:00:09\n37775.batch      FAILED      1:0   00:00:09</pre>\n    <p>Smallest relevant stderr excerpt:</p>\n    <pre>train.py: error: unrecognized arguments: --amp-dtype bfloat16 --grad-clip-norm 1.0\ntorch.distributed.elastic.multiprocessing.errors.ChildFailedError: Body-Tell/train.py FAILED</pre>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>Required Fixes</h2>\n    <ol>\n      <li>Make the required phase1 Slurm gate runnable. Either add compatible <code>--amp-dtype</code> and <code>--grad-clip-norm</code> support to <code>Body-Tell/train.py</code> and use them in training, or update the gate script/CLI contract so <code>sbatch slurm/body-tell-phase1.sh</code> completes successfully.</li>\n      <li>Fix runtime position encoding dtype under CUDA autocast/AMP. The position tensor must be returned in the same dtype as <code>memory</code> after operations such as <code>linspace</code>, <code>sin</code>, and <code>cos</code> that may promote under autocast.</li>\n      <li>Add or extend a GPU/AMP smoke test so a forward/loss/backward pass with the real aligned model and prefix load covers the dtype contract before the Slurm gate is retried.</li>\n    </ol>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>Residual Risk</h2>\n    <p>The loader itself is well constrained to the transformer decoder prefix. The remaining risk is in runtime training integration: the reviewer could not observe a successful checkpoint save path or full phase1 epoch because the gate fails at CLI parsing before training begins.</p>\n  </section>\n</main>\n</body>\n</html>\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_2","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,260p' Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\"","aggregated_output":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --ink: #17202a;\n      --muted: #5d6875;\n      --line: #d8e0e7;\n      --panel: #f6f8fa;\n      --soft: #eef4f7;\n      --accent: #14677b;\n      --warn: #9a4a17;\n      --bad: #993333;\n      --good: #276749;\n    }\n\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      color: var(--ink);\n      background: #ffffff;\n      font: 15px/1.62 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    header {\n      padding: 34px 42px 24px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\n      background: #f8fbfd;\n    }\n\n    main {\n      max-width: 1220px;\n      padding: 28px 42px 56px;\n    }\n\n    h1 {\n      margin: 0 0 8px;\n      font-size: 30px;\n      letter-spacing: 0;\n    }\n\n    h2 {\n      margin: 30px 0 12px;\n      font-size: 22px;\n      letter-spacing: 0;\n    }\n\n    h3 {\n      margin: 20px 0 8px;\n      font-size: 17px;\n      letter-spacing: 0;\n    }\n\n    p { margin: 8px 0; }\n\n    code {\n      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;\n      background: #edf3f7;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      padding: 1px 4px;\n      font-size: 0.92em;\n    }\n\n    pre {\n      overflow-x: auto;\n      background: #111827;\n      color: #f7fafc;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 14px 16px;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n\n    pre code {\n      background: transparent;\n      padding: 0;\n      color: inherit;\n    }\n\n    table {\n      width: 100%;\n      border-collapse: collapse;\n      margin: 12px 0 22px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n\n    th, td {\n      padding: 9px 10px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\n      vertical-align: top;\n    }\n\n    th {\n      text-align: left;\n      background: #f1f5f8;\n      color: #24313d;\n    }\n\n    ul, ol { padding-left: 22px; }\n    li { margin: 5px 0; }\n\n    .meta { color: var(--muted); }\n    .num {\n      text-align: right;\n      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n      white-space: nowrap;\n    }\n\n    .cards {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(190px, 1fr));\n      gap: 12px;\n      margin: 16px 0;\n    }\n\n    .card {\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      background: var(--panel);\n      padding: 14px 16px;\n    }\n\n    .card span {\n      display: block;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      font-size: 13px;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n\n    .card strong {\n      color: var(--accent);\n      display: block;\n      font-size: 22px;\n    }\n\n    .callout {\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);\n      background: var(--soft);\n      padding: 12px 14px;\n      margin: 12px 0 18px;\n    }\n\n    .warnbox {\n      border-left-color: var(--warn);\n      background: #fff7ed;\n    }\n\n    .badbox {\n      border-left-color: var(--bad);\n      background: #fff5f5;\n    }\n\n    .tag {\n      display: inline-block;\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      padding: 1px 8px;\n      font-size: 12px;\n      font-weight: 650;\n      white-space: nowrap;\n    }\n\n    .ok { color: var(--good); background: #eaf7ef; }\n    .warn { color: var(--warn); background: #fff2df; }\n    .bad { color: var(--bad); background: #ffe7e7; }\n    .info { color: var(--accent); background: #e7f3f7; }\n\n    @media (max-width: 860px) {\n      header, main {\n        padding-left: 20px;\n        padding-right: 20px;\n      }\n      table {\n        display: block;\n        overflow-x: auto;\n        white-space: nowrap;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <h1>Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</h1>\n    <p class=\"meta\">日期：2026-05-24；目标：让 Body-Tell 在结构和权重语义上尽量对齐 VoxTell v1.1，优先支持 VoxTell checkpoint 复用，而不是只做到 tensor shape 能加载。</p>\n  </header>\n\n  <main>\n    <section>\n      <h2>核验结论</h2>\n      <div class=\"callout\">\n        <p><strong>原差异报告中的核心不一致真实存在。</strong> 其中最影响 VoxTell 权重复用的是两类问题：一类是参数量和模块拓扑明显不同，例如 encoder/decoder；另一类是参数 shape 一致但 forward 语义不同，例如 transformer decoder。</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"cards\">\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>Body-Tell 当前参数</span><strong>328.98M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>VoxTell v1.1 参数</span><strong>440.03M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>Body encoder</span><strong>8.49M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>VoxTell encoder</span><strong>90.30M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>Transformer 参数</span><strong>251.86M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>最高风险</span><strong>shape 同而语义不同</strong></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr><th>差异点</th><th>核验结果</th><th>对权重复用的影响</th><th>证据位置</th></tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Transformer decoder</td>\n            <td><span class=\"tag bad\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 使用 <code>activation=\"gelu\"</code>，pre-norm path 执行 self-attention；VoxTell 默认 <code>relu</code>，active <code>forward_pre</code> 跳过 self-attention，只做 cross-attention 和 FFN。</td>\n            <td>参数名和 shape 可 100% 对上，但加载 VoxTell 权重后语义不等价。小模型同权重实验输出最大绝对差为 <code>0.9258</code>。</td>\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:69</code>、<code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:137</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:224</code></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Encoder backbone</td>\n            <td><span class=\"tag bad\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 5-stage 手写 ConvBlock；VoxTell 是 6-stage <code>ResidualEncoder</code>，features 为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320,320]</code>，blocks 为 <code>[1,3,4,6,6,6]</code>。</td>\n            <td>当前 encoder 无法复用 VoxTell encoder 权重，也很可能限制性能上限。这个差异不是“轻量配置”，而是 backbone 类型不同。</td>\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:155</code>、<code>VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1/plans.json:20</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:131</code></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Mask projections（含 <code>num_heads</code>）</td>\n            <td><span class=\"tag warn\">需区分 source default 和 checkpoint profile</span> Body-Tell 当前轻量结构会把 5 个 maskformer stage 截成 4 级；VoxTell 源码默认 <code>num_heads=1</code>，但 v1.1 predictor/checkpoint profile 实际使用 <code>num_heads=32</code>。</td>\n            <td>当前轻量 Body-Tell projection 输出为 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>；VoxTell v1.1 checkpoint profile 为 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>。这部分不参与 P6-lite；如后续做 full checkpoint 复用，必须以实际 checkpoint audit 为准，而不是只看源码默认值。</td>\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>、<code>:83</code>、<code>:89</code>；<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:74</code>、<code>:177</code>、<code>:370</code></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Decoder</td>\n            <td><span class=\"tag bad\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 4-stage 手写 decoder，<code>GroupNorm + GELU</code>；VoxTell 是 5-stage <code>VoxTellDecoder</code>，使用 <code>StackedConvBlocks</code> 并继承 encoder 的 <code>InstanceNorm3d + LeakyReLU + conv_bias=true</code>。</td>\n            <td>当前 decoder 无法复用 VoxTell decoder 权重。VoxTell 还总是构造 <code>seg_layers</code>，用于 checkpoint 兼容。</td>\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:174</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:280</code></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Position / memory 排列</td>\n            <td><span class=\"tag warn\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 动态生成 <code>D,H,W</code> 顺序的位置编码；VoxTell 使用 init 时固定的 <code>pos_embed</code> buffer，并用 <code>H,W,D</code> 顺序 flatten。</td>\n            <td>Body-Tell 当前 <code>volume_size=[128,128,256]</code>（见 <code>configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml:25</code>，当前数据集输入形状已调整到此尺寸）不是 192³。P6-lite 不加载 VoxTell <code>pos_embed</code>，但 runtime <code>pos</code> 必须和 VoxTell 的 <code>H,W,D</code> memory flatten 语义一致。</td>\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:118</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:185</code>、<code>:229</code></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </section>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2>目标状态</h2>\n      <p>新增一个 VoxTell-aligned 架构路径，而不是在现有轻量模型上做零散补丁。当前主目标收窄为复用 VoxTell <code>transformer_decoder.*</code> 权重；encoder、decoder、projection 和 full checkpoint 复用只作为后续可选实验，不作为本阶段 P6 目标。</p>\n\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr><th>模块</th><th>目标实现</th><th>权重复用要求</th></tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td><code>encoder</code></td>\n            <td>使用 <code>dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.residual_encoders.ResidualEncoder</code>，参数与 VoxTell v1.1 plan 一致。</td>\n            <td>P6-lite 不加载 <code>encoder.*</code>；可在后续 full-minus-pos_embed 实验中单独评估。</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td><code>decoder</code></td>\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
